keywordspec.doc:
Autosphere Framework library for cross platform clipboard management.

Will use `win32` package on Windows and `clipboard` package on Linux and Mac.

kw.doc:
Clear clipboard contents

Example:
    | Clear Clipboard |

Copy text to clipboard

:param text: to copy

Example:
    | Copy To Clipboard | text=Hello |

Paste text from clipboard

:return: text

Example:
    | ${text} | Paste From Clipboard |
